Running the Artificial Analysis Intelligence Index on V4 Pro (Reasoning, Max Effort) at first-party pricing costs ~$268, ~3x cheaper than Gemini 3.1 Pro Preview ($892), ~12x cheaper than GPT-5.5 (xhigh, $3,357), and ~19x cheaper than Claude Opus 4.7 ($5,117)

